---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Projects"
  description="Portfolio: Jules AI system, personality assessments, Discord server management, websites, and developer utilities."
>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Projects</h1>
    <p class="page-intro">Things I've built — solo, with AI, and for communities mainstream tech ignores.</p>

    <div class="projects-grid">

      <div class="project-card">
        <div class="card-header">
          <h3><a href="/jules/">Jules AI Collaborator</a></h3>
          <span class="status status-live">Live</span>
        </div>
        <p>
          Open-source AI operational system that runs my business. Content pipelines, research, scheduling, reporting, code. 18 custom skills, 5 hooks, cloud batch automation, and mobile access.
        </p>
        <div class="tech-tags">
          <span>Claude Code</span><span>Python</span><span>Bash</span><span>MCP</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card-links">
          <a href="/jules/">How it works &rarr;</a>
          <a href="https://github.com/jonathanmalkin/jules">GitHub &rarr;</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="project-card">
        <div class="card-header">
          <h3><a href="https://quiz.9archetypes.app">9 Archetypes Quiz</a></h3>
          <span class="status status-live">Live</span>
        </div>
        <p>
          Interactive personality assessment across 9 archetypes for adult audiences. Personalized email playbooks, partner comparison, and post-quiz survey. 200+ daily users.
        </p>
        <div class="tech-tags">
          <span>React</span><span>TypeScript</span><span>PHP</span><span>MySQL</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card-links">
          <a href="https://quiz.9archetypes.app">Take the quiz &rarr;</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="project-card">
        <div class="card-header">
          <h3>Discord Server Manager</h3>
          <span class="status status-archived">Archived</span>
        </div>
        <p>
          Suite of tools for a 300+ member community. Automated onboarding, role assignment, moderation tracking. Analytics with DAU/WAU/MAU, engagement funnels, health reports, dead channel detection. Permissions explorer for Discord's 7-layer hierarchy. DM export for archival.
        </p>
        <div class="tech-tags">
          <span>Python</span><span>TypeScript</span><span>discord.py</span><span>SQLite</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="project-card">
        <div class="card-header">
          <h3><a href="https://github.com/jonathanmalkin/builtwithjon">Websites</a></h3>
          <span class="status status-live">Live</span>
        </div>
        <p>
          builtwithjon.com and supporting sites. Zero JavaScript, hand-written CSS under 5KB. Auto-deploy on push. Full SEO layer: JSON-LD, sitemap, RSS, llms.txt. Domain management and email routing.
        </p>
        <div class="tech-tags">
          <span>Astro</span><span>Cloudflare Workers</span><span>CSS</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card-links">
          <a href="https://github.com/jonathanmalkin/builtwithjon">GitHub &rarr;</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="project-card card-wide">
        <div class="card-header">
          <h3>Utilities</h3>
          <span class="status status-mixed">Mixed</span>
        </div>
        <div class="utility-grid">
          <div class="utility-item">
            <strong>Whisper Repetition Fix</strong>
            <p>Homebrew wrapper intercepting whisper-cli with anti-repetition flags. Companion post-processor: 90+ hallucination filters, n-gram dedup, Claude Haiku fallback.</p>
            <div class="tech-tags">
              <span>Python</span><span>Homebrew</span><span>Claude API</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="utility-item">
            <strong>Event Distribution</strong>
            <p>AI-powered event creation with automated posting to 6 platforms. ChatGPT themes, DALL-E banners, RSVP management with location gating.</p>
            <div class="tech-tags">
              <span>TypeScript</span><span>OpenAI</span><span>REST APIs</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="utility-item">
            <strong>Plane Sync</strong>
            <p>Bidirectional markdown-to-Plane.so sync with cursor pagination, state reconciliation, and 1Password credentials.</p>
            <div class="tech-tags">
              <span>TypeScript</span><span>Plane API</span><span>1Password</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
